definitions.definition: To sew together so that the seam is scarcely visible; to sew up with skill and nicety; to finedraw .
To restore the original design of (a tapestry) by working in new warp .

main_definition: To sew together so that the seam is scarcely visible; to sew up with skill and nicety; to finedraw .
